README for polybar


INSTALL

  To get started with your own customization, you need to create a
  configuration file in ~/.config/polybar/config.ini.

  You can copy the default config from /etc/polybar/config.ini or start from
  scratch.

  For more information, see https://github.com/polybar/polybar/wiki


CUSTOMIZE BUILD


  This port comes with a minimal set of polybar modules. Supported modules
  will vary depending of your installation and features detected during the
  build.

  --  Module support:
  -- [X]   alsa
  -- [X]   curl
  -- [ ]   i3
  -- [ ]   mpd
  -- [X]   network (libnl)
  -- [ ]   pulseaudio
  -- [X]   xkeyboard

